title: Nosratabad-e Laklak
content:
Nosratabad-e Laklak (Persian: نصرت اباد لك لك, also Romanized as Noşratābād-e Laklak; also known as Noşratābād)[1] is a village in Jolgeh Rural District, in the Central District of Asadabad County, Hamadan Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 372, in 82 families.[2]
